POST-INSTALL:
		* Delete your personal "pluginreg.dat" (it will be generated automagically):

		# rm -rf ~/.mozilla/firefox/pluginreg.dat   (as root)
		$ rm -rf ~/.mozilla/firefox/pluginreg.dat   (or as normal user)

		* Symlink the library :
		# ln -s /usr/lib/mozplugger/mozplugger.so /MY_FIREFOX_INSTALL_DIR/plugins/

		* Restart Firefox

TEST:
		* Test the plugins by typing this address in Firefox:
		about:plugins
